-- Abris Buys Romanian Cargus From Deutsche Post DHL, Bursa Reports
-- B y   A n d r a   T i m u
-- 2012-10-23T06:20:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-23/abris-buys-romanian-cargus-from-deutsche-post-dhl-bursa-reports.html
Abris Capital Partners Sp. z o.o, a
private equity fund, bought Cargus Srl, a Romanian courier
company, from  Deutsche Post AG (DPW)  DHL, without disclosing the value
of the transaction,  Bursa  reported, citing the head of Abris’s
local unit.  Abris plans to invest about 450 million euros in Poland,
 Romania  and Ukraine, Cezar Scarlat, who heads the company’s
Romanian unit said, according to Bursa.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andra Timu in Bucharest at 
 atimu@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  